item.title: Page Builder
item.dc:creator: demoadmin
item.content:encoded:
﻿

Create Amazing Pages!

Choose from over 25 page modules! Now you can create awesome content in a matter of seconds. There's so many modules, you'll be spoilt for choice. Plus you can create parallax layouts on any page using the page builder![font_full1 title="ANIMATION" link="" icon="magic" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Animate any content and add effects from the animate.css library.[/font_full1][font_full1 title="MEDIA LIBRARY" link="" icon="desktop" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Add images straight from your media library. No more pasting image links![/font_full1][font_full1 title="BLOG CAROUSEL" link="" icon="comments" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Display your latest posts. Just add the module and select the category.[/font_full1][font_full1 title="NOTIFICATION BOXES" link="" icon="bullhorn" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Get your users attention with our awesome notification boxes. Simply add![/font_full1][font_full1 title="INDIVIDUAL ITEMS" link="" icon="picture" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Add portfolio, movie, client or testimonial item. There's modules for each![/font_full1][font_full1 title="SERVICE BOXES" link="" icon="ok" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Add any of the theme service boxes in 2 clicks. Add module & select style. Done![/font_full1][font_full1 title="GOOGLE MAPS" link="" icon="map-marker" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Ever wanted a full width Google Map? With this module its never been easier![/font_full1][font_full1 title="VIDEOS" link="" icon="film" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Import videos from your favourite sites just by pasting the video url.[/font_full1]

See the full-width Google map in action!

PLUS SO MUCH MORE!

Now it's easier than ever to create pages in seconds!

AWESOME FEATURES!

Minamaze comes with tons of awesome features! Including a powerful theme options panel, 100+ shortcodes and also an easy to use page builder. Make stunning websites easier and faster than ever before, all without touching a single line of code!
  • Page Builder

  • 2 Header Styles
  • Animation Effects
  • Responsive Layout
  • HD Retina Ready
  • Unlimited Colors
  • Easy To Customize
  • 1 Click Demo Installation
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlbnGSMJQbQ

Dedicated Support

We're always here to help. So if you ever have a question, just get in touch and we'll be on hand to assist. As a member you'll get support direct from the theme developers!

Powerful Features

Create stunning sites without touching a single line of code. Change everything from the color scheme to the site layout with just a few clicks. Never code again with Minamaze!

Professional Team

Developed by the awesome Think Up Themes team, you can always be sure that Minamaze has been developed to the highest standards.

MINAMAZE IS LIMITLESS!

NO NEED TO EVER CODE AGAIN!

[font_full1 title="Premium Support" link="#" button="" icon="life-ring" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Have a question? No problem! As a member you'll get support from the theme developers. Who better to help?[/font_full1][font_full1 title="Powerful Options" link="#" button="" icon="cogs" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Minamaze comes with a powerful options panel, now you can make hundreds of changes in seconds. It couldn't be easier![/font_full1][font_full1 title="Page Builder" link="#" button="" icon="wrench" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Create stunning pages without touching code using our awesome page builder. Just drag, drop and you're done![/font_full1][font_full1 title="1 Click Demo Installation" link="#" button="" icon="refresh" color="dark" size="small" background="off" spin="off"]Minamaze includes a 1 click demo installer. Use this to create a site just like this demo at the push of a button![/font_full1]

AWESOME FEATURES!

Minamaze comes with tons of awesome features! Including a powerful theme options panel, 100+ shortcodes and also an easy to use page builder. Make stunning websites easier and faster than ever before, all without touching a single line of code!
  • Page Builder
  • Powerful Theme Options Panel
  • 100+ Shortcodes
  • 2 Header Styles
  • Animation Effects
  • Responsive Layout
  • HD Retina Ready
  • Unlimited Colors
  • Easy To Customize
  • 1 Click Demo Installation
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TlbnGSMJQbQ

Dedicated Support

We're always here to help. So if you ever have a question, just get in touch and we'll be on hand to assist. As a member you'll get support direct from the theme developers!

Powerful Features

Create stunning sites without touching a single line of code. Change everything from the color scheme to the site layout with just a few clicks. Never code again with Minamaze!

Professional Team

Developed by the awesome Think Up Themes team, you can always be sure that Minamaze has been developed to the highest standards.

MINAMAZE IS LIMITLESS!

NO NEED TO EVER CODE AGAIN!

Our Skills

SKILL 1SKILL 2SKILL 3SKILL 4

Contact Us
